00:00:19,538 --> 00:00:21,879
So welcome to my talk about Subnautica

8
00:00:22,039 --> 00:00:25,142
and what that all meant to us and how we did it.

9
00:00:26,483 --> 00:00:28,824
Before I start, let me give a brief introduction

10
00:00:28,904 --> 00:00:32,567
to the game itself, if my slides are working.

